These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
Hobby: hiking, video-games, filmmaking, photography
Sport: skateboarding, volleyball, climbing, skiing
1. Hobby:filmmaking is between Sport:climbing and Sport:volleyball##2
2. Hobby:photography is on the left or right of Sport:climbing##3
3. Sport:climbing is not to the left of Sport:climbing##8
4. Sport:volleyball != Hobby:filmmaking##6
5. Hobby:filmmaking is somewhere to the right of Hobby:hiking##5
6. Hobby:hiking is on the right of Sport:skateboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | photography  | hiking | filmmaking | video-games  |
| Sport   | skateboarding | climbing   | skiing  | volleyball |

