.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
Food: cucumber, apricot, cauliflower, broccoli
Job: mechanic, librarian, electrician, videographer
1. Job:videographer is not to the left of Job:videographer##8
2. Food:cucumber is somewhere to the right of Food:broccoli##5
3. Food:cucumber == Job:librarian##1
4. Food:broccoli is between Food:cucumber and Food:apricot##2
5. Food:apricot is somewhere between Food:cauliflower and Job:mechanic##7
6. Job:electrician is somewhere to the left of Food:apricot##5
7. Job:mechanic is not to the left of Job:mechanic##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | cauliflower | apricot          | broccoli | cucumber     |
| Job    | electrician      | videographer | mechanic | librarian |

