.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
Job: engineer, analyst, mechanic, police-officer
Movie-Genre: documentary, fantasy, spy, animation
1. Movie-Genre:documentary is not to the left of Job:mechanic##8
2. Movie-Genre:fantasy is on the far left##1
3. Job:analyst is on the right of Job:engineer##1
4. Job:analyst is in an even position##4
5. Job:police-officer is on the far left or far right##3
6. Job:engineer is somewhere to the left of Movie-Genre:animation##5
7. Job:police-officer == Movie-Genre:spy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | engineer | analyst | mechanic     | police-officer |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy    | animation   | documentary | spy    |

