4. Music-Genre:gospel is not to the right of Sport:tennis##8
5. Music-Genre:punk == Sport:skiing##1
6. Music-Genre:punk is on the right of Sport:tennis##1
7. Music-Genre:pop is somewhere to the left of Music-Genre:gospel##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | pop   | indie         | gospel   | punk    |
| Sport         | cricket | biathlon | tennis | skiing |

