3. Transport:quad-bike is on the left or right of Music-Genre:punk##3
4. Music-Genre:r&b is somewhere to the right of Transport:train##5
5. Transport:car == Transport:car##1
6. Music-Genre:ambient != Transport:skateboard##6
7. Music-Genre:disco is not to the right of Music-Genre:ambient##8
8. Transport:train is not to the left of Transport:car##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | punk | ambient | r&b |
| Transport     | quad-bike | car       | train  | skateboard    |

